S.FORM: == kakiliman == Sen-ti-ya-ke, Sen-ti-ya-ke, anucaay Sen-tye-ke, nu Si-pang-ya a kamu anucaay Pu-taw-ya a kamu sakay Sen-ya-ke "Santiago", Si-pang-ya pangiha(san'tjaɣo)" a pangangan. zuma 15 se-ci Si-pang-ya bang-ci-huy nu bukesi "San Diego" a pangangan, nipabelin tuni a ngangan, anucaay u Sen-tye-ke, Sen-ti-ye-ke. Sen-ti-yake-Te-kung-pow-s-te-la "Si-pang-ya a ngangan Santiago de Compostela, imi u "mazeketay a bunac ulaulanganay a Sen-ti-ye-ke" nu Si-pang-ya Ka-li-si-ya sakakuay a kitizaan a cen-bu, tademaw caay ka katukuh tu 10 a emang. (Santiago,西班牙語發音:(san'tjaɣo))的稱呼.另外,以15 :Santiago de Compostela；意為" . nilaculan sikamu Ye-su 12 ku mikilulay cinizaan ci Ta-ya-ke itini mitadem, u tinsikiw kakatayzaan mibaung. makay se-ci hawsa, tulin sa ku tayniay mibaungan, katukuh i Ba-kow kasa kitizaanmakayni pasayza i Si-pang-ya saamisan masa caca singanganay a zazan nu mibaungay, Sen-ya-ke a zazan. Sen-ti-ya-ke -Te-kung-pow-s-tla sumamaday a tukuay I 1985 a mihcaan mapasisil u kitakitay lalangawan nu nisubelidan a zaysang. Si-pang-ya a labu atu Ba-kow a labuay " Sen-ya-ke a zazan" pasasumaen i 1993 a mihcaan atu 1998 a hihcaan mapasisil tusa a siyang cacayay a kitakit a lalangawan nu nisubelidan a zaysang. Sen-ti-yake-Te-kong-pow-ste-la cacay u mataliyukay nu buyu' ibatada nu adidi'ay a niyazu', Si-pang-ya a kmu kasikazan a ngangan u Sen-ti-yw-ke "Sen-ya-ke nu Si-pang-ya a kamu a ngangan", uyni a kitizaan i kung-yen 4 se-ci ayaw nanu Low-mw a tadem, 5 se-ci tu saayaway a mihca macalap nu Su-wi-bey a tademaw, 585 a nihcaan atu Su-wi-bey hunngti a kanatal u liwanzuma mapulung maenuc nu Li-aw-wi-ci-al-te "Liuvigild", mala nu Si-ke-te-hungti a kanatal nu sakaenem a sakuwan. kung-yen 711 a mihcaan, makayzaay saamis nu Bey tu cacayay nu Mu-s-lin a hitay itiza tu i Pu-low-tu capi nu Si-pang-ya tukus nu bayu tahkal. Si-ya-ke a Si-pang-ya hungti a kanatal malingatu tu cayay tu ku icelang, 7 a mihcaan hamin mataliyukay nu bayu a subal makayni piecaw, matalud matinenng mingayaw midebung mikuwan, nakamuan Sen-ya-ke natayza i Si-panga-ya musakamu tu nu kiwkay 7 a mihcaan, mapatay zikuz ya ukak tademen i Si-pang-ya. malakui' tu ku pinay a mihcaanz ikuz, u tadem niza nayay tu ku matinengay nu tademaw. katukuh 813 a mihcaan maazih tu nu malukay ku tadem zikuz, patizeng hantu nu tademaw tu cacay adidi'ay a kiwkay, pangangan hantu ku itiniay tu "Sen-ti-yake-Te-kung-pow-s-te-la", zumaTe-kung-pow-s-te-la nu La-tin a kamu "Campus Stellae" "bunac a ulaulangan" anucaay "Compositum" "tadem" a nisasuma. "Campus Stellae" 或者"Compositum" 演化來的. nikuz, Sen-ti-yake-Te-kung-pow-s-te-la mala nu Si-pan-ya mahiza u ciwlu, si-yen 10 se-citu sazikuzay a mihcaan, uyni a niyazu' namapeleng nu A-al-man mikeliday tu Mu-s-lin a hitay, nika kilul i 11 se-ci mahamin tu muliyaw mapatizeng, 12 se-ci tu sang-pan-ye, u balucu' patabaki tu icelang nu Ka-s-ti-li-ya hungti a kanatal atu Low-ma cyaw-tin a malecad ku balucu'. malingatu palahad tu pibaungan itini micunus tu sakay Si-pan g-ya tu kalilid nu kiwkay, sangaleb tulin tayni itini ku mibaungay, mahiza masa cacay u singanganay nu mibaungay a zazan nu Sen-ya-ke a zazan, a mililid ku Sen-ya-ke, Si-pang-ya i cung-se-ci a kitakitan u saicelangay, muliyaw malahad ku kesey, kahak atu nalimaan cacanan nu hekalay. nuayawan, labu nu tukay masinga' tu kunu makay cang-se-ci amalepun tu masanha' ku nipatizeng. . imahini, Sen-ti-yake-Te-kung-pow-s-te-la a tinsikiw nu tukay a singanganay a panutekan, Sen-ti-yake-Te-kung-pow-s-te-la a talakaway a cacudadan patizen g i 16 se-ci, saayaway angangan pasubana' tu sesiw, imahini 4 a emang ku mkicudaday pulung nu talakaway a cacudadan. 2013 a mihcaan 7 a bulad, tiniay nasikawaw pihacengay ku silamalay a satebuc. 如今, . malalitin tui hekalay atu zumaay a natinengan
